<div style="text-align: center;">
<h2><span>ENTRY REQUIREMENTS</span></h2>
<p>If you've created <strong><span style="text-decoration: underline;">at least three</span></strong> successful<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-1')">1</a></sup> pages (including SCP articles, tales, GoI-format documents, site dossiers, and artwork pages), please take the time to create an author page and take credit for your work. Create and tweak as you desire, and add yourself to the list above alphabetically by your <span style="text-decoration: underline;">wikidot username</span>.</p>
<p>The format for your slot is:</p>
<blockquote>
<p><span style="font-size:75%;"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">||[[*user&#32;YOURUSERNAME]]||[[[AUTHOR-PAGE-LINK&#32;|NAME-OF-LINK]]]||Personnel||</span></span></p>
</blockquote>
<p>See additional entries for more information.</p>
<p>You might also consider adding a chevron from a <a href="/list-of-foundation-s-internal-departments">Foundation Department</a> you are interested in, if applicable. If you have any questions or concerns regarding this database, or need assistance adding your information to it, please contact staff.</p>
